Sentencas: This paper exploits the suitability of three perovskite materials Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF), GdBaCo2O5+delta (GBC) and Ba0.5Sr0.5Mn0.7Fe0.3O3-delta (BSMF) as SOFC cathodes in the single-chamber configuration operating at the intermediate temperature range.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: TG analysis showed high thermal stability depending on the crystalline phases of the materials.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The catalytic activity of these three materials for hydrocarbon conversion was investigated under a realistic feed, i.e. with hydrocarbon, oxygen, water and carbon dioxide.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy of the various cathodes tested in symmetric cell configuration revealed a B-site dependence of the electrode catalytic activity for oxygen reduction.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: High temperature (1000 degrees C) powder reactivity tests over a gadolinium doped-ceria (CGO) and perovskite cathode revealed excellent chemical compatibility of BSMF and CGO.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Catalytic tests associated with thermal and structural characterization attest to the suitability of these materials in the single-chamber configuration.
Titulo: Alternative perovskite materials as a cathode component for intermediate temperature single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell
